parsed.plot: DEV: Rance and Talia consummated relationship—Talia's first sexual experience, marked by power exchange and degradation that resonated with suppressed aspects of her psychology. Rance used untrained Mage-Gift telekinetically (slammed door, closed curtains)—raw channels caused pain, demonstrated unpredictable power. PEND: How to present formalized connection to Selenay—semi-official arrangement known to Circle but hidden publicly.

entities.c: IDENTITY: Lost virginity to Rance—physical evidence includes bite mark. STANCE-Rance: Relationship transformed from political partnership to sexual/romantic bond. Discovered submissive desires—responds intensely to degradation, surrender of control. Psychological shift: found liberation in being dominated after lifetime of carrying responsibility. ARC: Acceptance that unprecedented connection with Rance is personal as well as political.

STANCE-Rance: Resigned acceptance of complications he creates. Concern about untrained Mage-Gift use—'leveling cottage would require extensive paperwork.' STANCE-Talia: Surprised by her response to domination—understanding of her need for surrender after years of responsibility. STATE: Unable to fully shield from bond during intimacy despite withdrawal attempt; positioned outside cottage as sentry.
